  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study defines a standardized protocol inspired to the ERAS philosophy for the&#xD;
      peri-operative treatment of patients undergoing emergency abdominal surgery. Primary endpoint&#xD;
      is the feasibility of the application of the standardized protocol; secondary endpoint is the&#xD;
      safety&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
